{"tid":95120,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"放底心事之深夜諗起EX","createTime":"2017-01-25T19:17:04.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-25T19:31:26.000Z","uid":7686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"944ee5abd411b0624e80c4d65e6b8ef1969933b2","tid":95120,"uid":7686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T19:17:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/4CL5_g5lud8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F4CL5_g5lud8&d=ZH4yc4t%2FNb3Zc6B%2FQrMq50sIbL4fERhwM0ZRx9Zc9p0%3D&h=feea1fd7\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/4CL5_g5lud8</a><br />\n在這爵士樂的伴奏下，一段段令人回味的回憶從我內心的深處裏被勾起。每一段回憶也盛載了一個故事，一個關於我和她所經歷的故事。可惜命運的紅線早已不再相交，如今我與她已經切切實實的成為陌生人。也許終有一天在內心深處的回憶會隨著時間所分解，但今夜可否讓我獨自沉醉在那回憶中嗎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54cbfa33d810dc5e8745396fb12e07e3cdf52517","tid":95120,"uid":7686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T19:20:19.000Z","msg":"有無巴絲入黎傾心事<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a294d51c50811df57c5914f54aded9b126073bc","tid":95120,"uid":5163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T19:21:24.000Z","msg":"打飛機啦"},{"pid":"11d143c0ce2532df5795bda3f8776afe79977a5f","tid":95120,"uid":7686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T19:24:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>打飛機啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n打左<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile_big.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"093c0b1080425b2147a7560e8f152fa17abebf11","tid":95120,"uid":7686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T19:31:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}